The famous role-playing saga The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim has collected more than two hundred different awards. And now it is time to enter a single edition, which includes not only the original game, but all the supplements thereto. Edition The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim. Legendary Edition is addressed to the most devoted fans of the series. It offers not only a game and three add-ons for it, but also various improvements - including a battle on horseback, new variants of finishing moves, an additional layer of complexity to the most experienced players, as well as "legendary" skills allow them to develop skills of the character forever.
